review:
Игра для тех, кто хочет убить время и подучить английский. Вот основные плюсы и минусы:

+Огромные скидки на распродажах (80-90%);
+Графика, а точнее стиль рисовки;
+Уровни сложности и возможность иметь несколько игровых файлов;
+Режим битв с боссами (подобие пантеонов и Зала богов из Hollow Knight);
+Хорошо сделанные битвы с боссами.

-Отсутствие русификатора;
-Непонятный сюжет;
-Трудно понять, чего от тебя хочет игра.

Примерно такие плюсы/минусы я выделил. Покупать или нет - решайте сами, но я бы порекомендовал.

 God, this game is so underrated. Yes, that is EXACTLY the word for this game, underrated. 
 I found it on a list of 'hidden gems of steam' on some site I don't remember, and I thought: ''Why wouldn't I give it a try? I can return it if I don't like it after all'' and boy, oh boy, I was wrong- in fact - so wrong, it EXCEEDED my expectations 100%:

 - it's got a great story-telling where everything your character says is your choice, even small actions like talking again to a character or doing certain things will actually trigger certain scenes; 
 - a cute mechanic in which you increase your health by being nice and doing sidequests, wich motivates you to explore;
 - collectibles in the game are actually useful, and again, motivate you to explore around;
 - a great soundtrack, made me even more excited while playing;
 - and, finally, E V E R Y T H I N G  IS  C U T E;

... and yet I haven't heard people playing it a lot, or even when searching for walkthroughs there aren't many... it makes me a bit sad that a game in which I can see that so much effort was put into doesn't get that much recognition.
 So would I recommend this game? Yes, totally. 10/10 play, recommend it your friends and your archenemies if they smell like food!!
